Message output:

Messages belong to categories.  These are defined in "warn.h" as an enum.  The
first parameter to __shmem_warn() is one of these values.

All categories are disabled initially, except for "FATAL".

To add a category:

1. add a value to the enum in "warn.h"

2. add a table entry to warnings[] in warn.c.
   0/1 means default disabled/enabled resp.

3. use it
